      "audioUrl": "audio/bebop_match_start_bebop_kelvin_convo03_03.mp3",
      "text": "Ms. Shelly loved reading about your adventures.  When you disappeared it was sad thinking  about her not being able to read a new one before she died.  But now that you're back there's hope for one more story.",
